---
title: Sweet Miso-Glazed Chicken & Sesame Rice with Ginger Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: This dish is a perfect combination of bright veggies, miso-glazed chicken and sesame-garlic rice, with the feel-good factor of creating a magnificent Asian-inspired meal from scratch.
